description: During the time of this recording, Sunny was working with violinist Stuff Smith and his trio. During a rehearsal with Stuff, Sunny brought out his new tape recording deck that recorded on paper tape. Many of these brittle but quality sound recordings have been preserved. Again, It's nice to hear Sunny telling his own story which is HIS-STORY unearthing the MYSTERY!
